PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of Nairn (Buz) Knott, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Export Development Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of John Humphries, whose term has expired.
